There are about 561 variables (observations) which are included in the features.txt.
Three other variables subjectID, activityID and activity were merged to the final data.
The final data shows the average of each variables for each activities performed by each partipants.
Transformations done to process the raw data:
1. Download data from source and read data
2. Merge data
3. Extract mean and std deviation for each measurement
4. Use descriptive activity names to name the activities in the data set
5. Appropriately labels the data set
6. Create a second independent tidy data set
